<h2>Holder for a singleton class.<br /></h2>
<div>Manages creation, deletion and access in a MT environment<br /> For protection, some operations will fail at compile time. For example, supposing MySingleton inherits Singleton&lt;&gt; :<source type="cpp">  int  main( void )
  {
      MySingleton&amp;  instance  =  MySingleton::Instance ();
      //  Here  we  viciously  try  to  delete  the  instance
      delete  &amp;instance;
      return  0;
  }
</source>
<br /></div>
